name: Dovetail Joinery - Barn Doors
description: Offer superior quality Oak doors, Floors
overview: Dovetail Joinery is the UK’s largest online supplier for real oak doors and floors. We possess over 35 years of wide experience and our family run business operates a traditional joinery workshop & sawmill in the Midlands. Our highly skilled team is committed towards quality craftsmanship with the excellent customer friendly service. We manufacture all our floors and doors in our own workshop with firm assurance that that you receive only the best quality oak. You can choose from a huge range of oak flooring styles at competitive prices.
